---
title: Mexican Black Bean Burritos with Cheddar Cheese & Smokey Aioli | Serves 2
description: There's nothing better than a good burrito that's ready in 15 minutes. Seriously, what could be better than warm flour tortillas
stuffed with all kinds of delicious fillings? Ours boast mildly spiced black beans, diced courgette, plus a
tomato salsa. Finish it off with a sprinkling of Cheddar for your Tex-Mex hit.
